# --------------------------------------------
# 11. QUICK REFERENCE
# --------------------------------------------

# CA (Certificate Authority) - certification center
#   Root CA - self-signed
#   Intermediate CA - signed by root

# PEM - certificate format (text, starts with -----BEGIN CERTIFICATE-----)
# KEY - private key (-----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----)
# CSR - certificate request (-----BEGIN CERTIFICATE REQUEST-----)

# Certificate fields:
#   CN (Common Name) - main name (www.dmz.ws.kz)
#   SAN (Subject Alternative Name) - additional names
#   AIA (Authority Info Access) - where to download CA certificate
#   CDP (CRL Distribution Points) - where to download CRL

# Validity:
#   Root CA - 10 years (3650 days)
#   Intermediate - 5 years (1825 days)
#   Server - 1 year (365 days)
